quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  29,64,"Wama hathihi alhayatuaddunya illa lahwun walaAAibun wa-inna addaraal-akhirata lahiya alhayawanu law kanooyaAAlamoon"
  29,65,"Fa-itha rakiboo fee alfulki daAAawooAllaha mukhliseena lahu addeena falammanajjahum ila albarri itha hum yushrikoon"
  29,66,"Liyakfuroo bima ataynahumwaliyatamattaAAoo fasawfa yaAAlamoon"
  29,67,"Awa lam yaraw anna jaAAalna haramanaminan wayutakhattafu annasu min hawlihimafabilbatili yu/minoona wabiniAAmati Allahiyakfuroon"
  29,68,"Waman athlamu mimmani iftaraAAala Allahi kathiban aw kaththaba bilhaqqilamma jaahu alaysa fee jahannama mathwan lilkafireen"
  29,69,"Wallatheena jahadoofeena lanahdiyannahum subulana wa-inna AllahalamaAAa almuhsineen"
  30,1,"Alif-lam-meem"
  30,2,"Ghulibati arroom"
  30,3,"Fee adna al-ardi wahum minbaAAdi ghalabihim sayaghliboon"
  30,4,"Fee bidAAi sineena lillahial-amru min qablu wamin baAAdu wayawma-ithin yafrahualmu/minoon"
  30,5,"Binasri Allahi yansuruman yashao wahuwa alAAazeezu arraheem"
